<h3>Compose email</h3>
<p>This is the first step for this plug-in, before sending mail  to user, first compose the mail using this page, once you created the mail from  this page, the created mail displayed automatically in the send mail page, <a target="_blank" href='http://www.gopiplus.com/work/2010/09/25/email-newsletter/'>Click here</a> to read more help.</p>
<h3>Send mail to registered user</h3>
<p>This page is to send mail to all registered user, in this  page you can find the all registered user with check box option, if you don&rsquo;t want  to send any mail to particular user, you can uncheck the email from the list, after  you selected the users from the list select the email subject and click send  mail button, <a target="_blank" href='http://www.gopiplus.com/work/2010/09/25/email-newsletter/'>Click here</a> to read more help.</p>
<h3>Send mail to comment posted user</h3>
<p>This page is to send mail to all comment posted user, in  this page you can find all the comment posted user with check box option, if  you don&rsquo;t want to send any mail to particular user, you can uncheck the email  from the list, after you selected the users from the list select the email  subject and click send mail button, <a target="_blank" href='http://www.gopiplus.com/work/2010/09/25/email-newsletter/'>Click here</a> to read more help.</p>
